CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778569553
OL,3,CAI-powered glasses and smart socks
OL,4,Ckeep dementia patients independent for
OL,5,Clonger
OL,7,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,8,FStew speaks to people with dementia
OL,9,Fwho are using AI-powered glasses and
OL,10,Fother new technology that's helping
OL,11,Fthem remain independent for longer
OL,13,FWhen Carole Greig was diagnosed with
OL,14,Fdementia, she was determined to do as
OL,15,Fmuch as possible to fight the disease.
OL,17,FShe signed up for trials and studies
OL,18,Fabout dementia with the aim of helping
OL,19,Fto grow our understanding of the
OL,20,Fdisease and what the solutions could
OL,21,Fbe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778569553
OL,3,CAI-powered glasses and smart socks
OL,4,Ckeep dementia patients independent for
OL,5,Clonger
OL,7,F"I have experienced cognitive decline
OL,8,Fand short-term memory is becoming an
OL,9,Fissue," she said. "I adopted a very
OL,10,Fpositive attitude after my diagnosis.
OL,12,F"I am still scared in my quieter
OL,13,Fmoments when I think about what is
OL,14,Fhappening to me, but the advancements
OL,15,Fof drugs and support are giving me
OL,16,Fhope and that hope is invaluable.
OL,18,F"It brings light to what could be a
OL,19,Fvery dark world."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778569553
OL,3,CAI-powered glasses and smart socks
OL,4,Ckeep dementia patients independent for
OL,5,Clonger
OL,7,FCarole has been involved in trials for
OL,8,Fa new technology called CrossSense -
OL,9,Fsmart glasses with a built-in AI
OL,10,Fpersonal assistant nicknamed 'Wispy'.
OL,12,FIt can identify everyday objects and
OL,13,Fhelp guide users through tasks like
OL,14,Fmaking a cup of tea and getting
OL,15,Fdressed or giving them reminders to
OL,16,Fcomplete jobs they may have forgotten.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778569553
OL,3,CAI-powered glasses and smart socks
OL,4,Ckeep dementia patients independent for
OL,5,Clonger
OL,7,FCarole's dementia is currently at a
OL,8,Fmild stage but she hopes that as the
OL,9,Fdisease progresses, the glasses will
OL,10,Fallow her to remain self-reliant for
OL,11,Flonger.
OL,13,F"Technology like the glasses is
OL,14,Fabsolutely paramount to keeping your
OL,15,Findependence," she said.
OL,17,F"I am so excited about them because
OL,18,Fyou do become isolated and you do lose
OL,19,Fconfidence when you realise that you
OL,20,Fcan't do what you used to do.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778569553
OL,3,CAI-powered glasses and smart socks
OL,4,Ckeep dementia patients independent for
OL,5,Clonger
OL,7,F"But with the technology, we can keep
OL,8,Fwalking in the world, keep being an
OL,9,Findividual, keep being us."
OL,11,FShe has invited the creators of the
OL,12,Fglasses to demonstrate them at her
OL,13,Fdementia support group, whose members
OL,14,Fare at various stages of the disease.
OL,16,F"I forget whether I have done things
OL,17,Flike shaving and teeth cleaning,"
OL,18,Fgroup member Leslie Price said. "It is
OL,19,Feasy to not be sure so having an
OL,20,Fassistant to prompt me would be really
OL,21,Fhelpful."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778569553
OL,3,CAI-powered glasses and smart socks
OL,4,Ckeep dementia patients independent for
OL,5,Clonger
OL,7,FAnother technology being demonstrated
OL,8,Fat the meeting is Smart Socks made by
OL,9,FMilbotix, which contain e-textile and
OL,10,Fsilicon sensors measuring pulse,
OL,11,Ftemperature, sweat, and motion.
OL,13,FThe socks are aimed at people whose
OL,14,Fdementia is more advanced and can help
OL,15,Fpredict and avoid falls.
OL,17,F"What you get is a live stream of the
OL,18,Fsock data as they are worn," said Dr
OL,19,FByron Creese from Brunel University
OL,20,Fwho is leading the research.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778569553
OL,3,CAI-powered glasses and smart socks
OL,4,Ckeep dementia patients independent for
OL,5,Clonger
OL,7,F"All these different biological
OL,8,Fmeasures can illustrate whether
OL,9,Fsomebody might be about to fall or
OL,10,Fwhether someone might be distressed or
OL,11,Fagitated."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThere is a growing sector of
OL,19,Ftechnology aimed at making it easier
OL,20,Ffor people with dementia to maintain
OL,21,Ftheir independence.
OL,26,@sD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
