FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778569553
OL,3,CAI-powered glasses and smart socks
OL,4,Ckeep dementia patients independent for
OL,5,Clonger
OL,7,FThe researchers behind the glasses
OL,8,Fhope that they could even help slow
OL,9,Fthe progression of the disease. They
OL,10,Fare still in the trial stage but
OL,11,FCrossSense aims to have them on the
OL,12,Fmarket by 2027.
OL,14,FNatasha Howard-Murray from Alzheimer's
OL,15,FSociety says embracing technology is
OL,16,Fkey to improving the lives of those
OL,17,Fwith dementia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
