PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778569553
OL,3,CAI-powered glasses and smart socks
OL,4,Ckeep dementia patients independent for
OL,5,Clonger
OL,7,F"There is no cure at the moment," she
OL,8,Fsaid. "And in research, we're working
OL,9,Freally, really hard while we wait for
OL,10,Fthat innovation and tech can really
OL,11,Fsupport people to live their everyday
OL,12,Flives."
